{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "427672fc-4635-4931-919f-0752cdf3c331",
    "name": "Joel RR06_Thieves",
    "sceneId": "84006d08-8e6d-4558-b9b5-101f3c3054fe",
    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "c8707bec-da4e-46ee-8573-500bd3f3267c",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "30b1d27f-ef45-4df4-be25-452bd4ff001a",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "61b56103-2e6a-4c54-8acb-6e7366e00e3e",
                            "text": "Ask About Joel",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5908441c-7d87-4a26-91f6-7aa026044f7b",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                    "text": "You seem to be taking this school thief thing personally.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e7711e5f-8e3c-4351-b5e5-72c1e489b278",
                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "This petty pilferer has turned the attention of the school to our class. Other students are wondering why we are to blame for the annoying crimes.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3c0cb09f-cab7-48aa-b7ae-83f59dc6b293",
                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "What is worse, Mr. Terk can use this as leverage to disband our Disbarred Bards class! We could all be kicked out of the castle.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "cf92138a-1cc4-42ad-8462-9af3dcb4cdd3",
                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "That would be most... unfortunate. This school enables me to research recent history in the rise and fall of the Sardonian Thieves Guild. I would have to return to Marete.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                                    "id": "4c06503b-b7a0-47be-9d9a-7c890f5f5c5c",
                                    "options": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "8d00c91a-687b-49cc-872a-169a2e9597a1",
                                            "text": "Ask About the Sardonian Thieves' Guild",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "0c25e433-220c-4791-8e69-ad147741c5c7",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                    "text": "What's so fascinating about a Thieves Guild?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "ee8464e8-815f-4cbd-b4f5-1b95688e5153",
                                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "At one point in time, every thief on this island belonged to the same guild. There was one Chief Thief in charge of it. Every crime on this island was committed under the auspices of the guild.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "06a81917-5390-4c46-ab06-9b620ef5aa83",
                                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Think of it - Sardonia was ruled by Thieves!",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "4",
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "c81ec0cf-c502-4149-aaa8-fe02b9800a75",
                                            "text": "Ask About Guild Research",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.changeTags",
                                                    "id": "0059138e-fc1e-472a-bca0-1aea7f411fbc",
                                                    "scope": "actor",
                                                    "scopeId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                                                    "tagsToAdd": "RavenRumor",
                                                    "tagsToRemove": null
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "f7d78e49-8af2-4e55-a51e-9df62ab6ebc4",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                    "text": "Why are you researching this Thieves Guild?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "9ee8db0e-3fcd-40df-8d17-44e87648da8a",
                                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "What united the thieves of this island wasn't just some charismatic Chief Thief... No, they united because of a symbol - the Raven statue. ",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "db4300c5-d6b3-4e0e-b2d8-f9828a407eec",
                                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "My father spent his life seeking such a statue. I came here to learn more about it.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "96d5308c-6578-4252-a076-2ea53260c527",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                    "text": "So what happened to this giant Thieves Guild? Caligari has at least three different guilds that I know of.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "eaf9e12a-aae1-4db4-8923-62e42c19d71b",
                                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "The last great Chief Thief died under mysterious circumstances and the Raven was never found. Intriguing, no?",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "6",
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "085f5b24-0191-44be-9a8e-23b6da8fd787",
                                            "text": "Ask About Marete",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "90c33e96-6684-4a53-bb3f-fb4fe4c12c57",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                    "text": "Why would you have to return to Marete if the school closes?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "e065cb26-5e51-40f2-bee5-4d5b7b701125",
                                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Alas, my funds are limited. It would be difficult for me to afford to stay in Sardonia if I had to pay for food and a place to live. This school is most useful to me.",
                                                    "emotion": "2",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "3",
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "AutoAddDone": true,
                                    "Unique": false
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "da399bfc-bf13-4ee1-9182-36cd99104f9e",
                            "text": "Ask About the School Thief",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7ecd2383-3da3-4754-a6dd-20971ad5774a",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                    "text": "Have you learned anything new about the thief?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5b2c929b-e13c-4713-b5a6-8b36e6617431",
                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Only that nothing of real value was stolen. Yes, the pilferer took a couple of musical instruments from the Bard practice room, some office supplies, a few personal items here and there. However, the thefts were minor at best.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9061e124-e302-463e-a3c7-e8b9b1b9c1d4",
                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "They certainly shouldn't be used as an excuse to shut down the Disbarred Bards class. I only hope that the Headmaster understands the trivialness of the situation.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "a0dbce63-f50a-4b10-b500-6303bad74127",
                            "text": "Say Goodnight",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "b4bd0a41-c63a-48f3-b05d-0dbe85071fa7",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                    "text": "I'll see you tomorrow.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "446368d0-402e-4b69-b221-45f4b8b0699a",
                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Good night, Mr. O'Conner. Let us hope that this 'school thief' issue blows over in the morning.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}